summary: This appears to be an email or internal communication from March 1, 2019, referencing contact information for a Deputy Chief in the Public Corruption Unit of the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York and a National Coordinator for Child Exploitation and Interdiction within the Office of the Deputy Attorney General (ODAG). The document is heavily redacted and minimal in content.
